    		</li>
    </ul>
    
    <hr />

    <h2>Basic Classes</h2>
    <p>
      While the point of this framework is to give basic styling to HTML without the need for CSS knowledge,
      for those that do have a basic knowledge of CSS, and want to add just a bit extra to their websites, 
      here are a few basic classes with examples.
    </p>
